Weather Website Project

Description
This project is a simple and intuitive weather website that provides users with current weather information for a specified location. The user-friendly interface allows anyone to quickly check the weather conditions, making it a handy tool for daily use.

Features

Current Weather Display: Get real-time updates on temperature, humidity, and wind speed.
Location-based: Enter the name of any city to retrieve accurate weather data.
Responsive Design: Access the website seamlessly on various devices, from desktops to mobile phones.


Technologies Used

HTML: Markup language for creating the structure of the website.
CSS: Stylesheet language for designing the layout and appearance.
JavaScript: Programming language for interactive and dynamic features.
Getting Started

Usage

Enter the name of the city or location for which you want to check the weather.
Click the "Enter" button to retrieve and display the current weather information.


Acknowledgments


Special thanks to Weather API for providing the weather data.
